NAME
        join - join a team

SYNOPSIS
	join <person>

DESCRIPTION
        With this command you join a team you have been invited into.
	When you enter a team, you will automatically switch to brief mode
	for as long as you follow your leader. You can still manually set it
	to verbose mode if you please.

OPTIONS
        person - a player in your presence

SEE ALSO
	invite, leave, options, team, teams
	For general information, see teams
